# IOUSBHIDReportDesc

## Declaration

```swift
struct IOUSBHIDReportDesc {
   UInt8 hidDescriptorType;
   UInt8 hidDescriptorLengthLo;
   UInt8 hidDescriptorLengthHi;
};
```

## Overview

USB HID Report Descriptor header. See the USB HID Specification at [link-1670329]. (This structure should have used the #pragma pack(1) compiler directive to get byte alignment.

## Related Documentation

- **IOUSBHIDReportDesc**: A structure that defines the USB HID report descriptor header.
